fields.title: ECB Policy Rates
fields.sql_query:
SELECT
    v.date,
    v.value,
    v.indicator_code
FROM macro_indicators_values v
JOIN macro_indicators_metadata m
    USING (indicator_code)
WHERE m.institution = 'ECB'
  AND m.indicator_type = 'policy rate'
ORDER BY v.date;

fields.title: Federal Policy Rates
fields.sql_query:
SELECT *
FROM macro_indicators_values
WHERE indicator_code IN ('DFEDTARL','DFEDTARU')
ORDER BY date

fields.title: FED Policy Rates

fields.title: Heatmap (Average Rates)
fields.sql_query:
SELECT
    v.date,
    v.value,
    m.indicator_code
FROM macro_indicators_values v
JOIN macro_indicators_metadata m USING (indicator_code)
WHERE m.indicator_type = 'money market rate'
ORDER BY v.date;

fields.title: Composite Index (5d MA)
fields.sql_query:
SELECT 
    v.date,
    v.indicator_code,
    v.value
FROM macro_indicators_values v
JOIN macro_indicators_metadata m USING (indicator_code)
WHERE m.indicator_type = 'money market rate'
ORDER BY v.date, v.indicator_code;

fields.title: Dispersion (Hybrid MAD, excl. JP/CN)
fields.sql_query:
SELECT v.date, v.value, m.indicator_code
FROM macro_indicators_values v
JOIN macro_indicators_metadata m USING (indicator_code)
WHERE m.indicator_type = 'money market rate'
  AND m.indicator_code NOT IN ('CHINA_FR001','CALL_RATE')
ORDER BY v.date;
